# RubyFPV Git Attributes
# ======================

# Text files
*.c text
*.cpp text
*.h text
*.hpp text
*.md text
*.txt text
*.cfg text
*.conf text
*.ini text
*.sh text
*.bat text
Makefile text

# Binary files
*.o binary
*.obj binary
*.exe binary
*.dll binary
*.so binary
*.a binary
*.lib binary
*.img binary
*.img.xz binary

# Scripts (make executable)
*.sh text eol=lf
*.bat text eol=crlf

# Documentation
*.md text
README* text
LICENSE text

# Configuration files
*.cfg text
*.conf text
*.ini text

# Build files
